description: Try our easy to follow Tray Bake recipe. Absolutely delicious with the best ingredients from Woolworths.
keywords: Seafood dishes,Pescatarian,Gluten free,Tree nut free,Egg free,Sesame free,Soy free,Wheat free,Dairy free,Peanut free
name: Tray Bake Recipe | Woolworths

recipeInstructions.text: Place the potatoes and olive oil in an oven proof dish, season with salt and pepper and roast for 20 minutes or until starting to brown
Add pumpkin, brussels sprouts, lemon wedges, garlic and rosemary sprigs. Return to the oven for another 20 minutes
Brush the salmon with olive oil, season with salt and pepper and arrange amongst the vegetables. Return to the oven for the final 10–15 minutes
Remove from oven and allow to rest for a few minutes before serving. Plate salmon with the roasted vegetables, garlic and lemon wedges from the pan and steamed greens on the side
